data.description:
Amazingly spacious bungalow: lots of upgrades & special features! Newer siding & 20 new windows! Massive open space in finished walk-up attic for 36-x-12-foot family room. Enter bright, glowing living rm to find a brick surround wdbrn fireplace. Wood floors in living rm, formal dining room.  The huge two baths totally remodeled with custom cabinetry! Master bth has Eurostyle whirlpool & shower! Kitchen also totally remodeled; incl. Bosch dishwasher only 4 yrs old! Kitchen & master bath boast Italian porcelain tile. Ceiling fans in both bedrms, living rm, & kitchen! Both bedrms w/ custom built-ins! Gas heat, central air conditioning. Finished attic has 2 window air conditioners. Full basement houses washer/dryer, laundry sink.
Tons of extra storage throughout home! Kitchen leads to large deck & backyard & 1-1/2 car detached, heated garage with window air cond. unit + storage loft.
